---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout active="home" title="Legion Services LLC | Built to Serve" description="Legion Services LLC is a veteran-owned company with Electrical, Aerial Operations, and Real Estate divisions.">
  <section class="hero home-hero">
    <div class="wrap hero-grid">
      <div><div class="eyebrow">Veteran-Owned Solutions Company</div><h1>Built to serve.<br />Equipped to deliver.</h1><p>Legion Services LLC unites specialized expertise across electrical contracting, aviation brokerage, and real estate support—under one professional, accountable organization.</p><div class="actions"><a class="btn" href="#divisions">Our Divisions</a><a class="btn outline" href="#contact">Contact Us</a></div></div>
      <div class="division-rail"><a href="/electrical"><span class="circle-icon">⚡</span><span><b>Electrical Division</b><br />Commercial, industrial, and government contracting.</span></a><a href="/aerial-operations"><span class="circle-icon">✈</span><span><b>Aerial Operations</b><br />Flight brokering, aircraft brokerage, and acquisition support.</span></a><a href="/real-estate"><span class="circle-icon">⌂</span><span><b>Real Estate Division</b><br />Sales, staging, photography, and drone mapping.</span></a></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="trust"><div class="wrap trust-grid"><div class="trust-item"><b>Veteran-Owned</b><span>Honor and disciplined execution</span></div><div class="trust-item"><b>Integrity Driven</b><span>Direct, transparent communication</span></div><div class="trust-item"><b>Client Focused</b><span>Solutions aligned to your goals</span></div><div class="trust-item"><b>West Virginia Proud</b><span>Serving the region and beyond</span></div></div></section>
  <section id="about" class="section"><div class="wrap split"><div><div class="eyebrow">One company. Three divisions.</div><h2>Practical expertise. Professional results.</h2></div><div><p>Legion Services was built around a simple standard: understand the mission, communicate clearly, and perform the work with accountability. Each division is focused on a distinct market while sharing the same leadership and commitment to quality.</p><p>Whether you are powering a facility, arranging an aircraft transaction, or preparing a property for market, Legion Services provides a capable and responsive point of contact.</p></div></div></section>
  <section id="divisions" class="section" style="background:var(--light)"><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head"><div class="eyebrow">Our Divisions</div><h2>Three divisions. One mission.</h2><p>Specialized services unified by a commitment to excellence.</p></div><div class="cards">
    <article class="card"><div class="card-visual">⚡</div><div class="card-body"><h3>Electrical Division</h3><p>Full-service electrical contracting for commercial, industrial, and government clients.</p><ul><li>Power distribution and installations</li><li>Maintenance and emergency response</li><li>Generators and energy systems</li></ul><a class="text-link" href="/electrical">Explore Electrical →</a></div></article>
    <article class="card"><div class="card-visual">✈</div><div class="card-body"><h3>Aerial Operations</h3><p>Flight brokering and aircraft brokerage supported by practical aviation knowledge.</p><ul><li>Private flight sourcing</li><li>Aircraft buyer and seller representation</li><li>Acquisition and market support</li></ul><a class="text-link" href="/aerial-operations">Explore Aviation →</a></div></article>
    <article class="card"><div class="card-visual">⌂</div><div class="card-body"><h3>Real Estate Division</h3><p>Licensed sales through Cornerstone Realty plus property marketing and support services.</p><ul><li>Buyer and seller representation</li><li>Staging and photography</li><li>Drone mapping and inspections</li></ul><a class="text-link" href="/real-estate">Explore Real Estate →</a></div></article>
  </div></div></section>
  <section class="contact-band"><div class="wrap"><div><b style="font-size:24px">Let’s build something great together.</b><br />Ready to discuss your project, aircraft, or property?</div><a class="btn outline" href="mailto:legionserviceswv@gmail.com">Contact Us Today</a></div></section>
</Layout>
